---
title: Chicken & Pesto Fettuccine alla Genovese with Garlic Bread & Mixed Leaf Salad
description: Presenting a few of our favourite things: juicy chicken, punchy pesto and golden ropes of fettuccine! All of this deliciousness is
tossed through with green beans, lemon and garlic for a bright and indulgent meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65c43e3a9d87f0bab617f99f-345d6b43.jpeg
